  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>原创 <span>每日发现最新LLM</span> <span>2026-03-20 18:47</span> <span style=\"display: inline-block;\">中国香港</span></p>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=06856678&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2FUibyxhuYSuFYd7p1vfBmNCyoXf6YgWibWdldGWlaGHWsAwA459IK80gC9WdFjbAwagTxbzUicYbH37Su6uul1yhdYwgEYrOUkjQ6FhTvxkPibvw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p>MoE模型Nemotron-Cascade-2，端到端文档智能模型Qianfan-OCR，用于视频处理的开源项目InSpatio-World，由Tongyi Lab开发的一个大型语言模型DeepResearch，面向多Agent项目的本地优先技能基础设施层MagicSkills，项目LatentChem，基于强化学习的项目HACRL</p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\">\n   <div style=\"line-height: normal;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"3 3 []\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.0859375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"640\" style=\"font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 389px;height: auto !important;\" data-imgfileid=\"100010333\" data-aistatus=\"1\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=17b00053&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_gif%2FGU2ibjU7TDkwuWicsSRFbFewfePZ1EiaVdtFvrJflfNa3P11kpGn8dhrOaAmmKQ3INqCXFZr2IrrUmmtkia9otecsw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p class=\"mp_profile_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-bottom: 24px;margin-top: 0px;\"><mp-common-profile class=\"custom_select_card mp_profile_iframe mp_common_widget\" data-pluginname=\"mpprofile\" data-nickname=\"机器之心SOTA模型\" data-alias=\"sotaai\" data-from=\"2\" data-headimg=\"http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/GU2ibjU7TDkyqTqr59u8fKegUibXxHSW3WF3ib6u8lQO8JicgNbPzicmhb8kPjrkYk6libDSD7ia1RlxQN9bWugwjguOg/0?wx_fmt=png\" data-signature=\"追踪 AI 开源进展，探索先进开发实践。\" data-id=\"MzkyMzcwMDIyMQ==\"></mp-common-profile></p>\n  </div>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🏆基座模型</span></strong></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"3 2 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Nemotron-Cascade-2</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5203703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"100018213\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1ab12fcf&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFaVkC2lcX1NdmKbRnG8UzLSia2jlnOLND8aTJoZO9PHn0EaRgK2WKhQ29dsY8ykBqtz2vtgvn04GJwUAMSBh31TfARQnccqwUUg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★</span></span><span data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">Nemotron-Cascade-2是一个开放的30B MoE模型，具有3B激活参数，提供强大的推理和Agent能力。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型从Nemotron-3-Nano-30B-A3B-Base后训练而来，在2025年国际数学奥林匹克竞赛（IMO）和国际信息学奥林匹克竞赛（IOI）中均获得金牌。它可以在思考和指令（非推理）模式下运行。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/nemotron-cascade-2\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/nemotron-cascade-2</a></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">②</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">项目：Qianfan-OCR</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5722222222222222\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"915\" data-imgfileid=\"100018205\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=50263bcc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFbFdRj5D6JghtooDwZCOiao6rtUd0kLKW5agLJZVDM6WFsOEFroFjvMKKThkcDQ5e9QHBavVYMxYkRJlVeJcqXUWycGwRprbQcA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★Qianfan-OCR是由百度Qianfan团队开发的一个4B参数的端到端文档智能模型。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它将文档解析、布局分析和文档理解统一在一个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">视觉语言架构</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">中。与传统的多阶段OCR流水</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">线不同，Qianfan-OCR直接执</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">行图像到Markdown的转换，并支持从结构化文档解析和表格提取到图表理解、文档问答和关键信息提取等广泛的提示驱动任务。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/qianfan-ocr\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/qianfan-ocr</a></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">③</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">项目：InSpatio-World</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5296296296296297\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"847\" data-imgfileid=\"100018202\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fc825909&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFaicCrjUian5Jc9HyWgfqoxaRkiauOvsLtw2RxJBS4uJbyboQdByYpK8Tcw8N01Ba6q1o62llnibfEjvbI0ulOX17FABDYHn8ADnbs%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★InSpatio-World是一个用于视频处理的开源项目，旨在通过多步骤的管道实现视频字幕生成、深度估计和视角合成。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该项目利用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">多个预训练模型</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">，包括视频字幕生成模型Florence-2和深度估计模型DA3，最终通过InSpatio-World模型进行视角合成。项目支持多种模型版本，适用于不同的计算资源需求。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p><span style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/inspatio-world\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/inspatio-world</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">④</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">项目：DeepResearch</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3907407407407407\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"625\" data-imgfileid=\"100018203\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=19539359&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFaC1MTL1KcbpJDlW8t2Geb6U2vdxAfcM229kYUR0bOAjcztEYlM1a7DricZyVgE3lYVhlKP0y7vgYOEsle2fBhC9uUrUxRkxedY%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★DeepResearch是由Tongyi Lab开发的一个大型语言模型，拥有30.5亿个总参数，其中每个token激活3.3亿个参数。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">该模型专为</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">长时间、深度的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">信息检索任务设计，展示了在多个Agent搜索基准测试中的最先进性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><a href=\"https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/deepresearch\" target=\"_blank\">https://sota.jiqizhixin.com/project/deepresearch</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"text-align: center;text-indent: 0px;font-weight: bold;font-size: 22px;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">🛠️ 框架平台、必备工具</span></p>\n  <p><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">①项目：MagicSkills</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.44351851851851853\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1600\" data-height=\"709\" data-imgfileid=\"100018204\" data-aistatus=\"1\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d65fd40b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FUibyxhuYSuFbfRicXj2TFhBgDHyicuHPhzAseuIBaXRcfAujzOC21JjOicMs65hr7AVq4uJicURvxDxx4wut0Mic40udlhu0AUWq59Xiagsj2x4TibA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">★MagicSkills是一个面向多Agent项目的本地优先技能基础设施层。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">它将分散的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">SKILL.md目录</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">转变为</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">可重用、可组合、可同步、可调用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: normal;\">的共享能力库。MagicSkills允许用户将技能安装到一个共享的技能池中，并将其组合成每个Agent的技能集合，支持通过一个稳定的API作为工具暴露。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: rgb(253, 240, 232);outline: 0px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">☆一键收藏：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;outline: 0px;color: rgb(37, 37, 37);font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;background-color: rgb(254, 254, 254);\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-family: Inter, &quot;Inter UI&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Source Han Sans SC&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, -apple-system, sans-serif, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, sans-serif;font-size: 16px;letter-spacing: normal;text-align: start;padding: 4px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);background-color: